{
  "//": "Locked-down profile for CI-failure investigation. Launch with: claude --settings .claude/settings.investigate.json. 'deny' wins over 'allow', so destructive actions are blocked even if some other settings file allows them. Read-only investigation commands run without prompts. For defense in depth, run this inside a throwaway git worktree and/or an environment with no push credentials.",
